    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>\"Soon will I rest, yes, forever sleep\"</em></p><h5 id=\"-strong-benefit-strong-\"><strong>Benefit:</strong></h5><p>Due to your impending demise you fight as if you have nothing to lose, since you kinda don't. Once per long rest when you would become bloodied you gain 1 Wof point.</p><h5 id=\"-strong-negative-strong-\"><strong>Negative:</strong></h5><p>When creating your character roll 3d4, then record the result. <br />After a number of years equal to the result your character will die, due to a cause of your chosing. (Ex, illness or curse)</p>",
